    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779070/extras/9e3124b8a0657590358a7e3e717001db.poster.avif?t=1707263903\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779070/extras/9e3124b8a0657590358a7e3e717001db.webm?t=1707263903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779070/extras/9e3124b8a0657590358a7e3e717001db.mp4?t=1707263903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>😼<strong>起床啦，该来一场猫咪大作战了</strong>😼<br>《Catnight》是一款多人在线游戏，是好友聚会的不二之选。你不仅要直面对手和空中满溢的毛茸茸子弹，还得在特殊的游戏环境中生存下来。每场比赛都充满活力，趣味十足。别忘了和队友并肩作战。朋友的陪伴会使乐趣翻倍。<br><br>😼<strong>并肩作战</strong>😼<br>从今往后，你将不再孤单一人。与好友组队，共同粉碎对手。占据信标，摧毁敌方核心。<br><br>😼<strong>玩家對抗環境</strong>😼<br>升级并获得新技能来击败敌人。 你可以独自争取胜利，但团队合作会更有趣。<br><br>😼<strong>多人在线</strong>😼<br>最美好的时刻，便是与三两好友相伴。所以即便朋友远在天边，你可以邀请他们共同游玩。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779070/extras/e9b6b2563371db821a7fa442da24b6fa.poster.avif?t=1707263903\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779070/extras/e9b6b2563371db821a7fa442da24b6fa.webm?t=1707263903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779070/extras/e9b6b2563371db821a7fa442da24b6fa.mp4?t=1707263903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>😼<strong>玩个痛快</strong>😼<br>是不是玩腻了TPP游戏？那《Catnight》对你再适合不过了。这款游戏将给你带来前所未有的快乐。轻松愉悦，仅有比赛需要稍显认真。系紧安全带，用猫咪武装自己。还在看吗？抓紧时间，开启你的探索之路。",
